iky%C5%AB%20Gardens%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688136cd85e81483682e8df2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrinking%20matcha%20tea%20at%20Hama-rikyu%20Gardens.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20similar%20refuge%20the%20following%20day%20as%20we%20made%20our%20way%20through%20Harajuku%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokyo-japan-souffle-pancakes-review-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%3C%2Fa%3E%20neighborhood%20also%20known%20to%20attract%20huge%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20walked%20past%20throngs%20of%20people%20at%20the%20famous%20Meiji%20Jingu%20shrine%2C%20we%20came%20across%20the%20Inner%20Garden.%20Measuring%20over%20890%2C000%20square%20feet%20and%20older%20than%20the%20shrine%20itself%2C%20the%20garden%20has%20something%20beautiful%20to%20see%20no%20matter%20the%20season.%20The%20beloved%20iris%20garden%20%E2%80%94%20featuring%20over%201%2C500%20plants%20%E2%80%94%20blooms%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20while%20the%20centuries-old%20Japanese%20maple%20trees%20turn%20stunning%20shades%20of%20orange%20and%20gold%20during%20autumn%20and%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20shrine%20was%20free%2C%20the%20Inner%20Garden%20required%20a%20separate%20entrance%20fee%20of%20500%20yen%2C%20or%20about%20%243.%20The%20extra%20cost%20seemed%20to%20keep%20out%20much%20of%20the%20crowd%2C%20as%20the%20garden%20was%20fairly%20empty%20when%20we%20visited.%20We%20easily%20found%20a%20bench%20by%20Nan-chi%20Pond%20and%20enjoyed%20the%20peace%20as%20we%20watched%20the%20water%20lilies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a07e66d0-7b75-4db9-9948-86dcdedb95ff%5C%22%3EHidden%20Kyoto%20gems%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20teahouse%20at%20Okochi%20Sanso%20Garden.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.in