3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20basically%20just%20took%20a%20huge%20bet%20that%20everyone%20is%20wrong%2C%20all%20the%20AI%20note%20takers%20are%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Courtne%20Marland%2C%20Lyra's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20you%20actually%20need%20to%20rebuild%20the%20conferencing%20platform%20itself%20because%20then%20you%20can%20control%20the%20entire%20screen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20meeting%20is%20scheduled%20in%20a%20virtual%20calendar%2C%20a%20link%20for%20a%20Lyra%20meeting%20is%20created%2C%20just%20like%20it%20is%20for%20existing%20meeting%20platforms.%20A%20team%20then%20has%20a%20call%20in%20which%20participants%20can%20collaborate%20on%20a%20screen%20share.%20Lyra's%20AI%20generates%20notes%20that%20can%20be%20shared%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%2C%20which%20is%20now%20valued%20at%20%2440%20million%2C%20was%20part%20of%20Y%20Combinator's%20spring%202025%20batch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20November%20launch%2C%20the%20company's%20revenue%20climbed%20from%20%2420%2C000%20to%20%24700%2C000%20in%20six%20weeks.%20Marland%20said%20Lyra%20is%20now%20powering%20over%20200%20hours%20of%20calls%20per%20week%20and%20competes%20with%20Zoom%2C%20Google%20Meet%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20Teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%246%20million%20seed%20round%20was%20led%20by%20468%20Capital%2C%20with%20participation%20from%20Rebel%20Fund%2C%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20and%20executives%20from%20companies%20like%20Ramp%2C%20Gusto%2C%20and%20Zapier.%20The%20round%20is%20Lyra's%20second%2C%20following%20a%20small%20pre-seed%20round%20in%20November%20with%20contributions%20from%20three%20angel%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELyra's%20product%20is%20priced%20on%20a%20pay-per-minute%20basis.%20Packages%20start%20at%20%246%2C000%2C%20which%20gets%20users%20about%20200%2C000%20minutes.%20Pricing%20is%20customized%20after%20this%20amount%2C%20but%20gets%20cheaper%20with%20more%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cash%20injection%2C%20Maland%20wants%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20startup's%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20is%20under%20stress%20because%20of%20quick%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20mission-critical%20software%2C%20which%20means%20people%20don't%20ever%20rip%20it%20out%20of%20their%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it%20needs%20to%20work%20100%25%2C%20all%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarland%20said%20that%20the%20company%20also%20wants%20to%20expand%20its%20go-to-market%20team%20by%20hiring%20engineers%2C%20product%20designers%2C%20and%20a%20head%20of%20growth.%20The%20company%20has%20a%20total%20of%205%20employees%2C%20including%20the%20two%20cofounders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%20pitch%20deck%20Lyra%20used%20to%20secure%20the%20fresh%20funding.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lyra%201%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880a3a485e81483682e8207%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lyra%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880a3a485e81483682e8209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lyra%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880a3a485e81483682e8208%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELyra%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lyra%204%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6880a5363d5881a51c1dd3d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22844%5C%22%3E%3Cfi