ect%20cycle%20includes%20four%20months%20of%20villager%20education%20and%20data%20gathering%2C%20followed%20by%20two%20months%20of%20mechanized%20pit%20digging%20before%20the%20monsoon.%20This%20ensures%20maximum%20impact%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%2C%20improving%20water%20conservation%20and%20reducing%20flood%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20community%20participation.%20Farmers%20volunteer%20through%20%3Cem%3Eshramdaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(collective%20labour)%20to%20fill%20the%20pits%20and%20provide%20materials%20like%20sand%2C%20pebbles%2C%20and%20stones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pre-%20and%20post-project%20impact%20is%20rigorously%20analysed%20by%20geologists%20and%20experts%20from%20the%20Groundwater%20Foundation%2C%20using%20photos%2C%20geotags%2C%20and%20scientific%20measurements%20of%20the%20water%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maharashtra%20JalTara%20groundwater%20recharge%20pits%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FDr-Vayal-second-from-left_11zon-1753180244.jpg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-474378%5C%22%20height%3D