0was%2020%20years%20ago.%20The%20second%20best%20time%20is%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20serene%20village%20of%20Sirkot%2C%20tucked%20away%20in%20the%20picturesque%20Bageshwar%20district%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20lives%20a%2060-year-old%20farmer%20whose%20life%20story%20is%20an%20inspiring%20testament%20to%20perseverance%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20environmental%20stewardship.%20Jagdish%20Chandra%20Kuniyal%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20the%20environment%20has%20not%20only%20transformed%20his%20own%20life%20but%20has%20uplifted%20his%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20four%20decades%2C%20he%20has%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20revive%20his%20land%2C%20plant%20trees%2C%20and%20create%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341870%2Fhygenco-first-green-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20futur%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341870%2Fhygenco-first-green-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%3Ee%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20despite%20countless%20challenges.%20His%20work%20came%20to%20national%20attention%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20programme%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMann%20Ki%20Baat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20praised%20Jagdish%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20a%20recognition%20that%20brought%20both%20joy%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20to%20the%20humble%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdish%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20personal%20loss.%20He%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20his%20life%20that%20left%20a%20deep%20impact.%20The%20tragedy%20could%20have%20crushed%20him%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20became%20the%20catalyst%20for%20a%20life%20built%20around%20resilience%20and%20a%20deep%20connection%20to%20the%20earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20a