oopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365774%2Fradhakrishnan-nair-rk-growing-urban-forests-miyawaki-method-ecosystem-plants-green-hero-of-india-gujarat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20arid%2C%20rocky%20soil%20of%20Sirkot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20the%20point%20of%20planting%20trees%20here%3F%20Nothing%20will%20grow%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20He%20kept%20pushing%20forward%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20belief%20that%20something%20better%20was%20possible%20for%20the%20land%20and%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20itself%20was%20as%20unforgiving%20as%20the%20doubts%20surrounding%20his%20endeavour.%20The%20farm%20was%20far%20away%20from%20his%20home%2C%20and%20every%20day%2C%20Jagdish%20had%20to%20trek%20almost%20five%20kilometres%20by%20foot%20to%20care%20for%20the%20young%20trees.%20As%20if%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20irregular%20rainfall%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20frequent%20destruction%20of%20his%20plants%20by%20wandering%20cattle%2C%20added%20to%20his%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20cattle%20from%20the%20village%20would%20roam%20through%20my%20fields%20and%20trample%20over%20the%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20numerous%20challenges%2C%20Jagdish%20remained%20undeterred%2C%20continuously%20finding%20innovative%20solutions.%20He%20dug%20deeper%20into%20the%20soil%2C%20reaching%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F272055%2Feco-friendly-home-generates-zero-water-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderground%20water%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20would%20help%20sustain%20his%20plants.%20Slowly%2C%20things%20began%20to%20improve.%20The%20trees%20started%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20as%20they%20did%2C%20the%20underground%20water%20levels%20began%20to%20rise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%